CSC442: Intro to AI
September 15, 2019
Authors:
 - Soubhik Ghosh (netid: sghosh13)
 - Rich Magnotti (netid: rmagnott)

Language: C++

Files in src/:
        README, Makefile, play.cpp, mancala.h, search.h, Mancala_Tester.py

Prerequisites:
	'make' utility
	g++ compiler with C++17 support
	python3 (Optional)

Build Instructions:
	- cd src/ (Go inside source directory)
	- make (Fire "make" command)

Output
	- play (binary file to run the game)
	- libplay.so (shared object file used by the python script)

Running Examples:
	- Human vs Human
	  ./play human human
	- Human vs Random
	  ./play human random
	- Random vs minimax
	  ./play random minimax
	- Alphabeta Pruning vs minimax
	  ./play alphabeta minimax
